text:
Anyone have an idea what could be causing the following Outlook rendering issue?
It's a linked image in a custom module:
Markup:
```
&lt;table class="banner-hero" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;
  {% if module.hero_image %}&lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td class="column hero-image"&gt;
      {{ module.hero_image_link.href ? '&lt;a href="'~module.hero_image_link.href~'" style="display: block; width: 100%;"&gt;' : '' }}
      &lt;img src="{{ module.hero_image.src }}" alt="{{ module.hero_image.alt}}" width="100%" style="display:block; margin-bottom: 0; width: 100%;"&gt;
      {{ module.hero_image_link.href ? '&lt;/a&gt;' : '' }}
    &lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;{% endif %}
  {% if module.hero_content %}&lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td class="hero-content"&gt;{{ module.hero_content }}&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;{% endif %}
&lt;/table&gt;
```
